  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté for about 1 minute until fragrant but not browned.",
    "Stir in cayenne pepper, lemon juice, and chopped herbs. Mix well to combine all ingredients.",
    "Add black olives into the pan and stir-fry them for another 2-3 minutes or until they're heated through and slightly softened.",
    "Remove from heat immediately to prevent overcooking of the olives which can make them too mushy."
